  m_Text: 'Demonstrates the usage of delegate coroutines and WaitAndExecute().


    Note
    the example on the left uses unscaled (=real) time, while the one on the right
    uses scaled (=in-game) Time. For this example, Time.timeScale is set to 0.5.

    Both
    variants are available for scaled and unscaled time.'
